PrecisAcceptance of an Instrument (REVOCATION OF DESIGNATION IN PART) wherein the MOWACHAHT/MUCHALAHT BAND (formerly the Nootka Band) revokes a 1963 Surrender insofar as it applies to a strip of land on Ahaminaquus Indian Reserve No. 12 in British Columbia, that will be transferred to the Province for highway purposes.

precis:
Acceptance of an Instrument (REVOCATION OF DESIGNATION IN PART) wherein the
MOWACHAHT/MUCHALAHT BAND (formerly the Nootka Band) revokes a 1963
Surrender insofar as it applies to a strip of land on Ahaminaquus Indian
Reserve No. 12 in British Columbia, that will be transferred to the
Province for highway purposes.
